					h1 The PI System enables Power Generation suppliers to better manage one unit or an entire fleet of generating units
					p A growing number of utility operators are considering the adoption of condition-based maintenance (CBM) and other proactive strategies that are driven by the actual condition of an asset rather than planned calendar- or time-based maintenance schedules. CBM promises to:
					ul
						li eliminate unnecessary maintenance
						li minimize unexpected failures
						li maximize use of resources
						li increase reliability and availability
						li support life extetnsion
